<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>PlanLib — AI Planning Problem Library</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;600&family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300;0,9..144,700;1,9..144,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
<link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ base }}static/index.css" />
</head>
<body>

<nav class="topbar">
  <div class="topbar-left">
    <a class="topbar-logo" href="{{ base }}">PlanLib</a>
  </div>
  <div class="topbar-nav">
    <a href="{{ base }}problems/">Problems</a>
    <a href="{{ base }}languages/">Languages</a>
    <a href="{{ base }}ipc/">IPC</a>
    <a href="{{ base }}tags/">Tags</a>
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#contribute">Contribute</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/planlib/planlib" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub ↗</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ── Hero ── -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-label">Planning Problem Library</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">A library for<br>AI planning benchmarks.</h1>
  <p class="hero-body">PlanLib documents classical planning benchmark domains — their formal definitions, complexity results, domain files, and instances — in one citable, open, community-maintained place.</p>
  <div class="hero-actions">
    <a href="{{ base }}problems/" class="btn-primary">Browse problems</a>
    <a href="#contribute" class="btn-ghost">Add a problem</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── Stats ── -->
<div class="stats">
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-value green">{{ stats.problems }}</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Problems</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-value green">{{ stats.domains }}</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Domain variants</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="stat-value green">{{ stats.instances }}</div>
    <div class="stat-label">Instances</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── What is PlanLib ── -->
<section class="section" id="about">
  <div class="section-label">About</div>
  <div class="section-title">What is PlanLib?</div>
  <p class="section-body">
    PlanLib is an open catalogue of AI planning benchmark domains, modelled after
    <a href="https://www.csplib.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent);border-bottom:1px solid #3a4a10;transition:border-color .15s" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--accent)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='#3a4a10'">CSPLib</a>
    for constraint satisfaction. Each entry documents the formal definition, complexity
    results, PDDL models, and benchmark instances of one planning domain. Problems are
    citable by their stable <span class="code-inline">probNNN</span> identifier, and
    contributions are open to anyone — no special tooling required.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- ── Contribute ── -->
<section class="section" id="contribute">
  <div class="contribute">
    <div>
      <div class="section-label">Contribute</div>
      <div class="section-title">Add a planning domain</div>
      <p class="section-body" style="margin-bottom:24px">
        Each problem lives in a folder with a few Markdown files —
        <span class="code-inline">general.md</span>, <span class="code-inline">references.md</span>,
        and a <span class="code-inline">domain.md</span> per variant.
        The scaffold command fills in all the structure; you just fill in the content.
        New entries are reviewed for correctness before being assigned a stable
        <span class="code-inline">probNNN</span> identifier.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap">
        <a href="https://github.com/planlib/planlib" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary">View on GitHub ↗</a>
        <a href="#" class="btn-ghost">Read the guide</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="terminal">
      <div class="terminal-title">Quick start</div>
      <div><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">git clone</span> <span class="t-arg">github.com/planlib/planlib</span></div>
      <div><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">python planlib_build.py new</span> <span class="t-arg">prob005-myslug</span></div>
      <div class="t-comment"># fill in the generated Markdown files</div>
      <div><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">python planlib_build.py build</span> <span class="t-arg">--all</span></div>
      <div><span class="t-prompt">$</span> <span class="t-cmd">gh pr create</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <span>PlanLib — AI Planning Problem Library</span>
  <span><a href="https://github.com/planlib/planlib" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a> · <a href="#">Cite</a> · <a href="#">Contact</a></span>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
